MANAGER, THE:

        On the preference screen, put the cursor over the main menu icon
        and press 'CTRL' and 'D'.  This should give evey player on your side
        99 strength and you will have $24,999,999.  Also, on the preference
        screen, hold down 'D', 'A', 'P', and 'G'.  This will give you lots
        of money and high statistics.
